
This game is a competitor to Sokoban.app which is toooooo ssssslllllooooowwww IMHO.
It also includes source, is for free and easier to play than any other Sokoban.... : ^ )

The newest version is always available on :
	ftp.informatik.uni-muenchen.de
	/pub/comp/platforms/next/Games/strategy/FastSokoban...


Version 1.01 differs from Version 1.00 
-	now there are 80 Levels instead of 50
-	hppa binary version on the ftp-site


Watch out for X-mas Sokoban in late 1994

The ball is stolen from		:	/NextDeveloper/Examples/AppKit/BreakApp/BreakView.m 
The levels are stolen from	:	the InterNet
the idea was taken from		:	XSokoban - which i played one year ago for 30 minutes.


